Module com.example.cab302assessment10b0101
Package com.example.cab302assessment10b0101.model

Class Collection

java.lang.Object
com.example.cab302assessment10b0101.model.Collection
public class Collection extends Object
The Collection class represents a collection of books associated with a specific user in the library management system. Each collection has a unique ID, a user ID, a name, and an optional description.
